Privacy Policy
Overview
This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is handled in AniMagic for iOS.
We Collect No Personal Information Using Our Applications
We do not collect, use, save, or have access to any of your personal data recorded in AniMagic for iOS.
Individual settings relating to AniMagic are not personal and are stored only on your device. You might also be asked to provide access to your photo library, but this is only so you can save your exports to your library. We don’t process that information at all and have no access to it.
Our Application Complies with the Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act
Our application doesn’t collect personal information from anyone, including children under the age of 13.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, feel free to get in touch with us at
hello@animagic.app